msgid "FAQ"
msgstr "常见问题"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeekOCR2.md:183
msgid ""
"**Q: Startup fails with HCCL port conflicts (address already bound). What"
" should I do?**"
msgstr ""
"**问：启动失败，提示HCCL端口冲突（地址已绑定）。该如何处理？**"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeekOCR2.md:185
msgid "A: Clean up old processes and restart: `pkill -f vLLM*`."
msgstr "答：清理旧进程并重启：`pkill -f vLLM*`。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeekOCR2.md:187
msgid "**Q: How to handle OOM or unstable startup?**"
msgstr "**问：如何处理OOM或启动不稳定问题？**"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeekOCR2.md:189
msgid ""
"A: Reduce `--max-num-seqs` and `--max-model-len` first. If needed, reduce"
" concurrency and load-testing pressure (e.g., `max-concurrency` / `num-"
"prompts`)."
msgstr ""
"答：首先减小`--max-num-seqs`和`--max-model-len`。如有必要，降低并发数和压测压力（例如`max-concurrency`/`num-prompts`）。"